title: The Beatles Covers - Phil's private collection
description:
Private collection of The Beatles&#039; songs performed by other artists. Different styles, different bands and artists, different languages - enjoy!

P.S. All songs that have ever been performed by The Beatles are considered "The Beatles songs", so if you don&#039;t really know that they performed "How Do You Do It" and "A Shot of Rhythm and Blues", don&#039;t complain, learn the history of the greatest band ever! :)
